            Spectrum News Text and Email Alerts Sign-up
        </a>
    
</div>
    <div class="pandoras-box">
        




    
    
    <div class="rich-text"><p>Get the latest news, sports and weather delivered straight to your inbox. <a href="https://my.textcaster.com/asa/Default.aspx?ID=3dfafa56-6952-4d0b-8b65-f1e8e6bf80da" target="_blank"><b>Click here to sign up for email and text alerts.&nbsp;</b></a></p>

</div>



    </div>
</div>

